arts.ttl: Cruz Hewitt, Leo Borg and others following their tennis parents
arts.sum: In 2023 Sebastian Korda reached the quarter-finals of the Australian Open, where 25 years earlier his father and former world number two Petr Korda won. Leo Borg's father Bjorn is one of tennis' all-time greats, having won 11 Grand Slam singles titles and spent 109 weeks at the top of the world rankings.
